{"tha-ap395:0.1":"Therapadana ","tha-ap395:0.2":"Pilindavacchavagga ","tha-ap395:0.3":"Sabbakittikattheraapadana ","tha-ap395:1.1":"“Kanikaramva jalitam, ","tha-ap395:1.2":"diparukkhamva ujjalam; ","tha-ap395:1.3":"Osadhimva virocantam, ","tha-ap395:1.4":"vijjutam gagane yatha. ","tha-ap395:2.1":"Asambhitam anuttasim, ","tha-ap395:2.2":"migarajamva kesarim; ","tha-ap395:2.3":"Nanalokam pakasentam, ","tha-ap395:2.4":"maddantam titthiye gane. ","tha-ap395:3.1":"Uddharantam imam lokam, ","tha-ap395:3.2":"chindantam sabbasamsayam; ","tha-ap395:3.3":"Gajjantam migarajamva, ","tha-ap395:3.4":"addasam lokanayakam. ","tha-ap395:4.1":"Jatajinadharo asim, ","tha-ap395:4.2":"braha uju patapava; ","tha-ap395:4.3":"Vakaciram gahetvana, ","tha-ap395:4.4":"padamule apattharim. ","tha-ap395:5.1":"Kalanusariyam gayha, ","tha-ap395:5.2":"anulimpim tathagatam; ","tha-ap395:5.3":"Sambuddhamanulimpetva, ","tha-ap395:5.4":"santhavim lokanayakam. ","tha-ap395:6.1":"‘Samuddharasimam lokam, ","tha-ap395:6.2":"oghatinnamahamuni; ","tha-ap395:6.3":"Nanalokena jotesi, ","tha-ap395:6.4":"navatam nanamuttamam. ","tha-ap395:7.1":"Dhammacakkam pavattesi, ","tha-ap395:7.2":"maddase paratitthiye; ","tha-ap395:7.3":"Usabho jitasangamo, ","tha-ap395:7.4":"sampakampesi medanim. ","tha-ap395:8.1":"Mahasamudde umiyo, ","tha-ap395:8.2":"velantamhi pabhijjare; ","tha-ap395:8.3":"Tatheva tava nanamhi, ","tha-ap395:8.4":"sabbaditthi pabhijjare. ","tha-ap395:9.1":"Sukhumacchikajalena, ","tha-ap395:9.2":"saramhi sampatanite; ","tha-ap395:9.3":"Antojalikata pana, ","tha-ap395:9.4":"pilita honti tavade. ","tha-ap395:10.1":"Tatheva titthiya loke, ","tha-ap395:10.2":"puthupasandanissita; ","tha-ap395:10.3":"Antonanavare tuyham, ","tha-ap395:10.4":"parivattanti marisa. ","tha-ap395:11.1":"Patittha vuyhatam oghe, ","tha-ap395:11.2":"tvanhi natho abandhunam; ","tha-ap395:11.3":"Bhayattitanam saranam, ","tha-ap395:11.4":"muttitthinam parayanam. ","tha-ap395:12.1":"Ekaviro asadiso, ","tha-ap395:12.2":"mettakarunasancayo; ","tha-ap395:12.3":"Asamo susamo santo, ","tha-ap395:12.4":"vasi tadi jitanjayo. ","tha-ap395:13.1":"Dhiro vigatasammoho, ","tha-ap395:13.2":"anejo akathankathi; ","tha-ap395:13.3":"Tusito vantadososi, ","tha-ap395:13.4":"nimmalo samyato suci. ","tha-ap395:14.1":"Sangatigo hatamado, ","tha-ap395:14.2":"tevijjo tibhavantago; ","tha-ap395:14.3":"Simatigo dhammagaru, ","tha-ap395:14.4":"gatattho hitavabbhuto. ","tha-ap395:15.1":"Tarako tvam yatha nava, ","tha-ap395:15.2":"nidhivassasakarako; ","tha-ap395:15.3":"Asambhito yatha siho, ","tha-ap395:15.4":"gajarajava dappito’. ","tha-ap395:16.1":"Thometva dasagathahi, ","tha-ap395:16.2":"padumuttaram mahayasam; ","tha-ap395:16.3":"Vanditva satthuno pade, ","tha-ap395:16.4":"tunhi atthasaham tada. ","tha-ap395:17.1":"Padumuttaro lokavidu, ","tha-ap395:17.2":"ahutinam patiggaho; ","tha-ap395:17.3":"Bhikkhusanghe thito sattha, ","tha-ap395:17.4":"ima gatha abhasatha. ","tha-ap395:18.1":"‘Yo me silanca nananca, ","tha-ap395:18.2":"saddhammancapi vannayi; ","tha-ap395:18.3":"Tamaham kittayissami, ","tha-ap395:18.4":"sunatha mama bhasato. ","tha-ap395:19.1":"Satthi kappasahassani, ","tha-ap395:19.2":"devaloke ramissati; ","tha-ap395:19.3":"Anne devebhibhavitva, ","tha-ap395:19.4":"issaram karayissati. ","tha-ap395:20.1":"So paccha pabbajitvana, ","tha-ap395:20.2":"sukkamulena codito; ","tha-ap395:20.3":"Gotamassa bhagavato, ","tha-ap395:20.4":"sasane pabbajissati. ","tha-ap395:21.1":"Pabbajitvana kayena, ","tha-ap395:21.2":"papakammam vivajjiya; ","tha-ap395:21.3":"Sabbasave parinnaya, ","tha-ap395:21.4":"nibbayissatinasavo’. ","tha-ap395:22.1":"Yathapi megho thanayam, ","tha-ap395:22.2":"tappeti medinim imam; ","tha-ap395:22.3":"Tatheva tvam mahavira, ","tha-ap395:22.4":"dhammena tappayi mamam. ","tha-ap395:23.1":"Silam pannanca dhammanca, ","tha-ap395:23.2":"thavitva lokanayakam; ","tha-ap395:23.3":"Pattomhi paramam santim, ","tha-ap395:23.4":"nibbanam padamaccutam. ","tha-ap395:24.1":"Aho nuna sa bhagava, ","tha-ap395:24.2":"Ciram tittheyya cakkhuma; ","tha-ap395:24.3":"Annatanca vijaneyyum, ","tha-ap395:24.4":"Phuseyyum amatam padam. ","tha-ap395:25.1":"Ayam me pacchima jati, ","tha-ap395:25.2":"bhava sabbe samuhata; ","tha-ap395:25.3":"Sabbasave parinnaya, ","tha-ap395:25.4":"viharami anasavo. ","tha-ap395:26.1":"Satasahassito kappe, ","tha-ap395:26.2":"yam buddhamabhithomayim; ","tha-ap395:26.3":"Duggatim nabhijanami, ","tha-ap395:26.4":"kittanaya idam phalam. ","tha-ap395:27.1":"Kilesa jhapita mayham, ","tha-ap395:27.2":"bhava sabbe samuhata; ","tha-ap395:27.3":"Sabbasava parikkhina, ","tha-ap395:27.4":"natthi dani punabbhavo. ","tha-ap395:28.1":"Svagatam vata me asi, ","tha-ap395:28.2":"…pe… ","tha-ap395:28.3":"katam buddhassa sasanam. ","tha-ap395:29.1":"Patisambhida catasso, ","tha-ap395:29.2":"…pe… ","tha-ap395:29.3":"katam buddhassa sasanam”. ","tha-ap395:30.1":"Ittham sudam ayasma sabbakittiko thero ima gathayo abhasitthati. ","tha-ap395:31.1":"Sabbakittikattherassapadanam tatiyam. "}